Mindlance's emphasis on *balance, purpose, and growth* and its commitment to being *mindful* so its actions support balance in the work and societal ecosystem strongly resonates with me. I am excited by the opportunity to contribute to that mission through dependable engineering support for critical public-sector data services. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting.

